s%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-sirens-blasts-sound-across-israel-after-iran-fires-drones-missiles-5437170%5C%22%3Ebarrage%20of%20drones%20and%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20first-ever%20direct%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20territory.%20Similar%20aerial%20attacks%20occurred%20last%20year%20when%20Hamas%20launched%20Operation%20'Al-Aqsa%20Flood'%20and%20conducted%20aerial%20and%20ground%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Israel%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20stated%2C%20%26quot%3BDozens%20of%20surface-to-surface%20missile%20launches%20from%20Iran%20were%20identified%20approaching%20Israeli%20territory.%20The%20IDF%20Aerial%20Defense%20Array%20successfully%20intercepted%20the%20majority%20of%20the%20launches%20using%20the%20Arrow%20Aerial%20Defense%20System%2C%20together%20with%20Israel's%20strategic%20allies%2C%20before%20they%20crossed%20into%20Israeli%20territory.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-video-israels-iron-dome-intercepts-swarm-of-iranian-missiles-5437221%5C%22%3EVideos%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20%3C%2Fa%3Eshow%20the%20Arrow%20defense%20system%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20intercepting%20aerial%20threats.%20The%20night%20sky%20lit%20up%20with%20multiple%20explosions%20across%20Israel%2C%20with%20no%20signs%20of%20tensions%20simmering%20down%20between%20the%20regional%20powers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20is%20the%20Arrow%20Aerial%20Defense%20System%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Aerospace%20Industries%2C%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20US%20Missile%20Defence%20Agency%2C%20produced%20the%20Arrow%20Defence%20System%2C%20a%20surface-to-surface%20missile%20system%20forming%20an%20upper%20tier%20in%20Israel's%20multi-layered%20air%20defence%20system.%20Development%20began%20in%20the%20late%201980s%20as%20a%20joint%20effort%20between%20Israel%20and%20the%20US.%20The%20Arrow%201%20system's%20technology%20demonstrator%20underwent%20at%20least%20seven%20flight%20tests%20in%20the%201990s%20and%20was%20further%20developed%20to%20form%20a%20lighter%20missile%20known%20as%20Arrow%202%2C%20which%20was%20inducted%20in%202000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20induction%20of%20Arrow%202%20missiles%20in%20the%20air%20defence%20arsenal%20gave%20Israel%20the%20capability%20to%20intercept%20short%20and%20medium-range%20missiles%20with%20its%20hit-and-kill%20approach%20in%20the%20upper%20atmosphere.%20The%20objective%20is%20to%20neutralize%20the%20incoming%20missile%20before%20its%20descent%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIron%20Dome%2C%20David's%20Sling%2C%20and%20the%20Arrow%20Defence%20System%20create%20a%20layered%20defence%20system.%20The%20Iron%20Dome%20system%2C%20which%20has%20been%20battle-tested%20in%20the%20past%2C%20was%20actively%20deployed%20to%20intercept%20drones%20and%20short-range%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ERead%20more%3A%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-palestine-hamas-gaza-iron-dome-how-israel-defends-its-skies-from-rocket-attacks-4460636%5C%22%3EHow%20Hamas%20Outfoxed%20Israel's%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20A%20Nearly%20Impenetrable%20Air%20Defence%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Does%20the%20Arrow%20Defence%20System%20Work%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arrow%202%20was%20inducted%20into%20the%20air%20defence%20arsenal%20in%202000%2C%20and%20the%20advanced%20Arrow%203%20system%20is%20intended%20to%20destroy%20long-range%20targets%20in%20the%20atmosphere.%20The%20rocket%20has%20a%20two-stage%20solid-propellant%20booster%20enabling%20it%20to%20reach%20speeds%20of%20Mach%209%20(nine%20times%20the%20speed%20of%20sound).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defence%20system%20consists%20of%20the%20missile%20launcher%2C%20the%20EL%2FM-2080%20Green%20Pine%20fire%20control%20radar%20(FCR)%2C%20a%20Hazelnut%20Tree%20Launch%20Control%20Center%20(LCC)%2C%20and%20a%20Citron%20Tree%20battle%20management%20centre.%20The%20Green%20Pine%20radar%20provides%20long-range%20target%20detection%20capability%20and%20can%20intercept%20multiple%20targets%2C%20allowing%20the%20missile%20to%20take%20on%20a%20maximum%20of%2014%20targets.%20The%20FCR%20can%20also%20counter%20electronic%20jamming%20of%20systems.%20The%20radar%20provides%20an%20effective%20range%20of%202%2C400%20kilometres%20and%20can%20strike%20targets%20at%20altitudes%20of%20100%20km.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20radar%20constantly%20detects%20incoming%20threats%20towards%20the%20territory.%20Once%20a%20target%20is%20detected%2C%20real-time%20information%20is%20relayed%20to%20the%20control%20centre%20regarding%20the%20estimated%20trajectory%20of%20the%20target%2C%20its%20speed%2C%20and%20if%20the%20missile%20is%20heading%20toward%20a%20strategic%20target%20like%20cities%20or%20military%20establishments%2C%20the%20missile%20is%20launched.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20missile%20is%20vertically%20launched%2C%20and%20the%20two-stage%20booster%20powers%20the%20rocket%20to%20Mach%209.%20The%20finned%20kill%20vehicle%20in%20the%20rocket%20can%20focus%20its%20blast%20in%20the%20direction%20specified%20by%20the%20missile%20seeker.%20If%20it%20fails%20to%20strike%20the%20target%2C%20the%20fragmentation%20warhead%20can%20explode%20within%2040%20metres%20of%20the%20target.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arrow%20rocket%20is%20based%20on%20the%20principle%20of%20using%20Kinetic%20Energy%20as%20a%20weapon%20of%20destruction.%20The%20hypersonic%20speed%20of%20the%20Arrow%20rockets%20can%20allow%20it%20to%20be%20used%20as%20an%20anti-satellite%20weapon.%20The%20Arrow%20defence%20system%20is%20compatible%20with%20the%20US%20Patriot%20Missile%20Defence%20System%2C%20providing%20interoperability.%20The%20missiles%20can%20be%20launched%20from%20silos%2C%20canisters%2C%20and%20each%20launcher%20consists%20of%20six%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fexecutivegov.com%2Farticles%2Farrow-3-interceptor-missile-system-the-ultimate-layer-of-defense%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520Arrow%25203%2520Interceptor%2520Missile%2520System%2520adapts%2520a%2520compact%2520and%2Cof%2520mass%2520destruction%2520(WMD).%5C%22%3EArrow%203%20defence%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20latest%20addition%20to%20Israel's%20air%20defence%20capabilities%20to%20intercept%20long-range%20threats.%20It%20was%20first%20tested%20in%202015%20and%20was%20put%20to%20use%20last%20year%20in%20November%20when%20it%20successfully%20intercepted%20and%20destroyed%20a%20ballistic%20missile%20launched%20by%20Houthis%20in%20Yemen%20over%20the%20Red%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Arrow%203%20rockets%20neutralize%20targets%20in%20the%20exo-atmosphere%20before%20the%20ballistic%20missile%20enters%20the%20re-entry%20stage.%20Videos%20on%20social%20media%20platforms%20show%20the%20Arrow%20system%20intercepting%20Iranian%20missiles%20in%20the%20exo-atmosphere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20conventional%20hit-and-kill%20technology%20of%20rockets%20that%20rely%20on%20liquid%20or%20gas%20propulsion%2C%20the%20Arrow%203%20has%20a%20conventional%20rocket%20motor%2C%20and%20once%20launched%2C%20its%20trajectory%20can%20be%20adjusted.%20Though%20Arrow%203%20is%20the%20latest%20addition%2C%20in%20April%202021%2C%20Israel%20admitted%20that%20it%20failed%20to%20intercept%20Syrian%20missiles%20on%20multiple%20occasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20has%20funded%20roughly%20half%20of%20the%20annual%20development%20costs%20of%20the%20Arrow%202%20system.%20By%202020%2C%20the%20total%20U.S.%20financial%20contribution%20toward%20the%20Arrow%20Weapon%20System%20exceeded%20%243.7%20billion.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713066420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fhgmo9uig_iran-attacks-israel_625x300_14_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-war-explained-how-israel-countered-irans-aerial-attack-with-arrow-missiles-5437654%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Air%20raid%20s