dia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsolomon-islands-readies-for-election-in-shadow-of-chinas-influence%2Famp_articleshow%2F109281421.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fsolomon-islands-readies-for-election-in-shadow-of-chinas-influence%2Famp_articleshow%2F109281421.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Unpopular%20Rishi%20Sunak%20In%20'Doom%20Loop'%20As%20UK%20PM%20Stares%20At%20Election%20Defeat%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EHe's%20failed%20to%20meet%20key%20pledges%2C%20hit%20an%20opinion%20poll%20low%2C%20and%20even%20cramped%20the%20style%20of%20a%20popular%20Adidas%20shoe%3A%20Britain's%20beleaguered%20Conservative%20leader%20Rishi%20Sunak%20appears%20destined%20to%20lose%20a%20looming%20general%20election.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETwo%20tax%20cuts%20and%20a%20slightly%20improving%20economy%20have%20failed%20to%20boost%20Sunak's%20political%20fortunes%2C%20while%20criticism%20from%20ex-prime%20minister%20Boris%20Johnson%20and%20speculation%20over%20Brexit%20figurehead%20Nigel%20Farage's%20intentions%20are%20adding%20to%20his%20woes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolitical%20scientist%20Rob%20Ford%20reckoned%20Sunak%20has%20been%20left%20looking%20%26quot%3Bhapless%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20face%20of%20seemingly%20unstoppable%20political%20momentum%20away%20from%20his%20ruling%20Tories.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20the%20herd%20moves%2C%20it%20moves.%20There's%20not%20much%20you%20can%20do%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%2C%2043%2C%20has%20yet%20to%20announce%20the%20date%20of%20the%20election.%20He%20is%20expected%20to%20call%20it%20for%20October%20or%20November%20but%20is%20legally%20allowed%20to%20wait%20until%20January%20at%20the%20latest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESurveys%20overwhelmingly%20show%20that%20Britons%20want%20an%20end%20to%2014%20years%20of%20Tory%20rule%2C%20and%20nothing%20that%20Sunak%20has%20done%20since%20he%20became%20PM%2018%20months%20ago%20appears%20to%20be%20changing%20their%20minds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20YouGov%20poll%20released%20this%20month%20found%20that%20the%20Conservatives%20would%20win%20just%20155%20seats%20in%20the%20UK%20parliament%2C%20down%20from%20the%20365%20that%20they%20won%20under%20Johnson%20at%20the%20last%20election%20in%20December%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKeir%20Starmer's%20opposition%20Labour%20Party%20would%20win%20403%20seats%2C%20the%20same%20survey%20found%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20whopping%20154-seat%20majority.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRight%20now%2C%20it's%20very%20difficult%20to%20see%20how%20the%20Conservatives%20remain%20in%20government%20after%20the%20next%20election%20simply%20because%20of%20the%20scale%20of%20shift%20they%20need%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Keiran%20Pedley%2C%20director%20of%20politics%20at%20polling%20firm%20Ipsos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Moving%20the%20dial'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20succeeded%20Liz%20Truss%20in%20October%202022%20after%20Tory%20MPs%20forced%20her%20out%20following%20a%20disastrous%2049%20days%20in%20office%2C%20during%20which%20her%20mini-budget%20spooked%20financial%20markets%2C%20sank%20the%20pound%20and%20sent%20mortgage%20payments%20skywards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20had%20followed%20Johnson%2C%20who%20himself%20had%20been%20defenestrated%20by%20colleagues%20following%20a%20series%20of%20scandals%2C%20including%20over%20illegal%20parties%20in%20Downing%20Street%20during%20Covid-19%20lockdowns.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20turmoil%20of%20the%20two%20previous%20administrations%20has%20hamstrung%20Sunak%2C%20political%20analysts%20say%20he%20has%20also%20contributed%20to%20his%20own%20plight%20by%20falling%20short%20on%20promises%20and%20failing%20to%20connect%20with%20voters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20promising%20to%2C%20he%20has%20not%20stopped%20migrants%20arriving%20from%20France%20on%20small%20boats.%20National%20Health%20Service%20waiting%20lists%20are%20higher%20than%20when%20he%20took%20office.%20Economic%20growth%20is%20stagnant%2C%20although%20inflation%20has%20more%20than%20halved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20has%20also%20tried%20a%20number%20of%20leadership%20and%20policy%20resets%20that%20have%20fallen%20flat%2C%20including%20watering%20down%20carbon%20net%20zero%20commitments%20in%20a%20pitch%20to%20motorists%20and%20recently%20talking%20about%20extremism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rightward%20tilt%20comes%20as%20the%20fringe%20Reform%20UK%20party%20threatens%20to%20deprive%20the%20Conservatives%20of%20key%20seats%2C%20particularly%20if%20Farage%20stands%20for%20them%20as%20he%20has%20teased.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B(Sunak%20has)%20been%20trying%20to%20find%20this%20magic%20wand%20or%20silver%20bullet%20to%20turn%20things%20around%20but%20at%20the%20moment%20none%20of%20it%20seems%20to%20be%20moving%20the%20dial%2C%26quot%3B%20Pedley%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20Ipsos%20poll%20published%20in%20March%20found%20that%2058%20percent%20of%20voters%20view%20the%20Conservatives%20unfavourably%2C%20the%20highest%20percentage%20this%20parliament.%20Only%2019%20percent%20view%20them%20favourably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20gave%20Sunak%20a%20net%20favourability%20rating%20of%20minus%2038%2C%20the%20lowest%20of%20any%20politician%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E-%20'Rather%20awkward'%20-%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECritics%20often%20accuse%20the%20wealthy%20ex-financier%20of%20being%20out%20of%20touch%20with%20average%20Britons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20is%20a%20combination%20of%20being%20rather%20awkward%20and%20nerdy%2C%20and%20then%20if%20challenged%20he%20always%20sounds%20really%20irritable%2C%26quot%3B%20Ford%2C%20politics%20professor%20at%20Manchester%20University%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESunak%20is%20striving%20to%20revive%20his%20party's%20fortunes%2C%20traversing%20the%20country%20to%20meet%20voters%20as%20rumours%20swirl%20that%20a%20disastrous%20showing%20in%20local%20elections%20on%20May%202