aused%20light%20damage%20to%20one%20Israeli%20military%20facility%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Dying%20Mother%20Handed%20Over%20Baby%20In%20Sydney%20Mall%20Stabbing%20Rampage%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20midst%20of%20a%20Sydney%20mall%20stabbing%20rampage%2C%20witnesses%20say%20a%20fatally%20wounded%20mother%20handed%20over%20her%20injured%20nine-month-old%20baby%20to%20a%20stranger%20to%20save%20the%20infant's%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStories%20of%20courage%20are%20still%20emerging%20from%20Saturday's%20attack%2C%20in%20which%20a%2040-year-old%20knifeman%20with%20mental%20illness%20roamed%20the%20packed%20shopping%20centre%2C%20killing%20six%20people%20and%20seriously%20wounding%20a%20dozen%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELone%20senior%20police%20officer%20Amy%20Scott%20is%20being%20hailed%20for%20tracking%20down%2C%20and%20then%20shooting%20dead%20the%20assailant%20during%20his%20killing%20spree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20young%20man%20was%20filmed%20fending%20off%20the%20attacker%20on%20an%20escalator%2C%20armed%20only%20with%20a%20shopping%20centre%20bollard.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStorekeepers%20opened%20their%20doors%20to%20shelter%20frightened%20shoppers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20harrowing%20story%20of%2038-year-old%20mother%20Ashlee%20Good's%20desperate%20final%20act%20to%20save%20her%20baby%20daughter%20Harriet%20has%20struck%20a%20chord%20with%20many%20shocked%20Australians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWitnesses%20told%20local%20media%20she%20was%20heard%20screaming%20when%20the%20assailant%20approached%20her%20in%20the%20shopping%20complex.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20baby%20got%20stabbed%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20man%20at%20the%20scene%20with%20his%20brother%20told%20Channel%209%20News%20in%20the%20aftermath%20of%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20mum%20got%20stabbed%20and%20the%20mum%20came%20over%20with%20the%20baby%20and%20threw%20it%20at%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithin%20hours%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20police%20said%20the%20toll%20had%20climbed%20to%20six%20after%20Good%20died%20in%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20baby%20is%20still%20in%20%26quot%3Ba%20serious%20but%20stable%20condition%26quot%3B%20in%20hospital%2C%20New%20South%20Wales%20police%20assistant%20commissioner%20Anthony%20Cooke%20said%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20to%20Australian%20media%2C%20Good's%20family%20described%20her%20as%20%26quot%3Ba%20beautiful%20mother%2C%20daughter%2C%20sister%2C%20partner%2C%20friend%2C%20all%20round%20outstanding%20human%20and%20so%20much%20more%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20two%20men%20who%20held%20and%20cared%20for%20our%20baby%20when%20Ashlee%20could%20not%20--%20words%20cannot%20express%20our%20gratitude%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20child%2C%20they%20said%2C%20was%20%26quot%3Bdoing%20well%26quot%3B%20after%20%26quot%3Bhours%20of%20surgery%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESky%20News%20Australia%20television%20reporter%20Laura%20Jayes%20was%20near%20tears%20as%20she%20revealed%20on%20air%20that%20she%20knew%20the%20sixth%20victim%2C%20who%20she%20described%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bincredible%20athlete%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can%20tell%20you%20that%20it%20was%20a%20mother%2C%20a%20mother%20in%20the%20prime%20of%20her%20life%2C%20a%20new%20mother%20with%20a%20nine-month-old%20baby%2C%26quot%3B%20Jayes%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20imagine%20her%20needing%20to%20hand%20over%20the%20most%20precious%20thing%20in%20her%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHer%20baby%20went%20to%20surgery%20and%20her%20mum%20didn't%20make%20it.%20So%20that's%20really%20hard%20news%20to%20take.%20And%20I%20am%20bringing%20you%20that%20not%20knowing%20about%20the%20other%20five%20victims.%20But%20there's%20one%20victi