20Priorities.%20Iranian%20state%20media%20said%20the%20country%20had%20also%20fired%20ballistic%20missiles%2C%20which%20may%20be%20far%20more%20powerful%20and%20fly%20in%20a%20high%20arc%20before%20hitting%20their%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20US-backed%20system%20of%20interconnected%20radar%20and%20mobile%20missile%20batteries%20is%20designed%20to%20shoot%20down%20rockets%2C%20missiles%20and%20mortars%20that%20could%20hit%20Israeli%20population%20centers%20or%20important%20infrastructure.%20It%20has%20been%20lauded%20for%20reaching%20a%2090%25%20interception%20rate%20in%20past%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20and%20UK%20forces%20also%20sought%20to%20repel%20the%20attack.%20A%20US%20defense%20official%20said%20its%20forces%20in%20the%20region%20shot%20down%20Iranian-launched%20drones%20targeting%20Israel%2C%20while%20the%20UK%20Defense%20Ministry%20said%20it%20deployed%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20jets.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20will%20likely%20carefully%20monitor%20the%20Israeli%20and%20US%20response%20to%20see%20how%20its%20technology%20competes%20with%20Western%20air%20systems%20and%20tactics%2C%20according%20to%20a%20former%20US%20intelligence%20official%2C%20who%20asked%20not%20to%20be%20identified%20given%20the%20sensitivity%20of%20the%20issue.%20Iran%20could%20use%20those%20insights%20for%20future%20attacks%2C%20as%20well%20as%20share%20it%20with%20proxies%20to%20improve%20their%20effectiveness%20with%20Iranian%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20well-known%20of%20Israel's%20air%20defences%20is%20Iron%20Dome%2C%20which%20has%20shot%20down%20thousands%20of%20rockets%20since%202011%20but%20is%20limited%20to%20a%20short%20range.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael%20also%20has%20a%20medium-to-long-range%20interceptor%20known%20as%20David's%20Sling%2C%20plus%20the%20Arrow%20defense%20system%2C%20which%20is%20designed%20to%20intercept%20missiles%20fired%20from%20as%20far%20away%20as%202%2C400%20kilometers.%20That%20range%20includes%20Iran%2C%20as%20well%20as%20Yemen%2C%20Syria%20and%20Iraq%2C%20where%20militant%20groups%20allied%20with%20Iran%20are%20based.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slow-moving%20drones%20are%20meant%20%26quot%3Bto%20confuse%20the%20radar%20systems%20in%20Israel%20and%20then%20make%20sure%20that%20the%20missiles%20that%20would%20follow%20the%20drones%20would%20hit%20their%20intended%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20avoiding%20the%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20humiliation%26quot%3B%20of%20all%20its%20projectiles%20being%20shot%20down%2C%20said%20Ali%20Vaez%2C%20Iran%20project%20director%20at%20the%20International%20Crisis%20Group.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713059580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F49pv3qu_israel-iron-dome-reuters-_625x300_14_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-tensions-iran-attack-tests-limits-of-us-backed-israeli-air-defenses-5437348%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Early%20signs%20suggest%20Israel's%20vaunted%20air%20defenses%20passed%20their%20biggest%20test%20yet%2C%20repelling%20an%20unprecedented%20barrage%20from%20Iran%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-tensions-iran-attack-tests-limits-of-us-backed-israeli-air-defenses-5437348%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-tensions-iran-attack-tests-limits-of-us-backed-israeli-air-defenses-5437348%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fisrael-iran-tensions-iran-attack-tests-limits-of-us-backed-israeli-air-defenses-5437348%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Sydney%20police%20identify%20knife%20attacker%20who%20killed%20six%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published