20young%20man%20around%20his%20game%20and%20what%20he%20needs%20to%20do.%20He%20has%20been%2C%20I%20think%2C%20unfairly%20put%20into%20a%20bracket%20where%20he%20has%20been%20called%20slow.%20But%20you%20have%20to%20have%20context%20to%20some%20of%20these%20stats.%20We%20know%20that%20it%20is%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20sometimes%20getting%20these%20things%20up%20onto%20the%20screen.%20But%20he%20is%20fine.%20He%20is%20playing%20conditions%20well.%20The%20last%20game%20(CSK%20vs%20KKR)%20was%20a%20great%20example%20of%20how%20a%20leader%20plays%2C%20and%20there%20is%20class%20as%20well.%20I%20have%20absolutely%20no%20doubt%20about%20Ruturaj%2C%26quot%3B%20Fleming%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20five%20matches%2C%20Gaikwad%20has%20scored%20155%20runs%20in%20IPL%202024%20at%20an%20average%20of%2038.75%20and%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20117.42.%20He%20has%20scored%20just%20one%20half-century%2C%20with%20the%20best%20score%20of%2067*.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFleming%20said%20that%20though%20batting%20has%20evolved%20in%20the%20IPL%20over%20the%20year%2C%20there%20needs%20to%20be%20something%20that%20helps%20bowlers%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBatting%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20has%20evolved%20at%20a%20huge%20rate%20of%20knots%2C%20the%20last%20five%20years%20in%20particular.%20So%20now%20you%20are%20seeing%20some%20unbelievable%20skill.%20The%20challenge%20of%20the%20IPL%2C%20from%20a%20skill%20point%20of%20view%2C%20is%20how%20the%20bowlers%20can%20even%20the%20game%20up%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Fleming.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20two%20bouncers%20(rule)%20is%20one%2C%20and%20maybe%20we%20need%20to%20keep%20looking%20at%20other%20ways%20to%20do%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFleming%20said%20that%20his%20team%20looks%20forward%20to%20this%20highly-anticipated%20fixture%2C%20which%20has%20turned%20into%20a%20fine%20rivalry%20due%20to%20the%20team's%20success%20over%20the%20years.%20Both%20sides%20