https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fmilitants-block-highway-in-balochistan-kill-11%2Farticleshow%2F109280792.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fmilitants-block-highway-in-balochistan-kill-11%2Famp_articleshow%2F109280792.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fpakistan%2Fmilitants-block-highway-in-balochistan-kill-11%2Famp_articleshow%2F109280792.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Explained%3A%20Who%20Are%20Revolutionary%20Guards%2C%20Group%20That%20Calls%20The%20Shots%20In%20Iran%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIran's%20elite%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20launched%20a%20drone%20attack%20against%20targets%20in%20Israel%20on%20Saturday%2C%20Iranian%20English-language%20press%20TV%20cited%20Iranian%20sources%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20commander%20in%20the%20Corps'%20Quds%20force%2C%20Mohammad%20Reza%20Zahedi%2C%20had%20been%20killed%20on%20April%201%20in%20an%20airstrike%20on%20Iranian%20diplomatic%20premises%20in%20the%20Syrian%20capital%2C%20Damascus%2C%20that%20Iran%20blamed%20on%20Israel%2C%20prompting%20Iranian%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei%20to%20vow%20revenge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20are%20some%20questions%20and%20answers%20about%20the%20IRGC%2C%20Iran's%20dominant%20military%20force%2C%20which%20has%20its%20own%20army%2C%20navy%2C%20air%20force%20and%20intelligence%20wing%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20IRGC%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20set%20up%20shortly%20after%20the%201979%20Islamic%20Revolution%20to%20protect%20the%20Shi'ite%20Muslim%20clerical%20ruling%20system%20and%20provide%20a%20counterweight%20to%20the%20regular%20armed%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20answers%20to%20Supreme%20Leader%20Ayatollah%20Ali%20Khamenei.%20The%20IRGC%20has%20an%20estimated%20125%2C000-strong%20military%20with%20army%2C%20navy%20and%20air%20units.%20It%20also%20commands%20the%20Basij%20religious%20militia%2C%20a%20volunteer%20paramilitary%20force%20loyal%20to%20the%20clerical%20establishment%20that%20is%20often%20used%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20anti-government%20protests.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBasijis%20mounted%20%26quot%3Bhuman%20wave%26quot%3B%20attacks%20against%20Iraqi%20troops%20during%20a%20war%20in%20the%201980s.%20In%20peacetime%2C%20they%20enforce%20Shi'ite%20Iran's%20Islamic%20social%20codes.%20Analysts%20say%20Basij%20volunteers%20may%20number%20in%20the%20millions%2C%20with%201%20million%20active%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Quds%20Force%20is%20the%20IRGC's%20overseas%20arm%20%2C%20which%20heavily%20influences%20its%20allied%20militias%20across%20the%20Middle%20East%2C%20from%20Lebanon%20to%20Iraq%2C%20Yemen%20and%20Syria.%20Its%20members%20have%20fought%20in%20support%20of%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad%20in%20Syria's%20civil%20war%20and%20have%20backed%20Iraqi%20security%20forces%20in%20their%20battle%20against%20Islamic%20State%20militants%20in%20recent%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIts%20top%20commander%2C%20Major-General%20Qassem%20Soleimani%2C%20was%20killed%20by%20the%20United%20States%20in%20a%20drone%20attack%20in%20Iraq%20in%202020%20that%20raised%20fears%20of%20a%20major%20conflict.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IRGC%2C%20branded%20a%20terrorist%20group%20by%20the%20United%20States%2C%20has%20sought%20for%20years%20to%20shape%20the%20Middle%20East%20according%20to%20Iran's%20interests.%20In%201982%2C%20it%20founded%20the%20heavily%20armed%20Shi'ite%20political%20movement%20Hezbollah%20in%20Lebanon%20as%20a%20vehicle%20to%20export%20Iran's%20Islamic%20Revolution%20and%20fight%20Israeli%20forces%20that%20had%20invaded%20Lebanon%20that%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHezbollah%20is%20now%20a%20major%20military%20force%20that%20has%20played%20a%20role%20in%20regional%20conflicts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20ARE%20THE%20IRGC'S%20MILITARY%20CAPABILITIES%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IRGC%20oversees%20Iran's%20ballistic%20missile%20programme%2C%20regarded%20by%20experts%20as%20the%20largest%20in%20the%20Middle%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Guards%20have%20used%20the%20missiles%20to%20strike%20Sunni%20Muslim%20militants%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iranian%20Kurdish%20opposition%20groups%20in%20northern%20Iraq.%20The%20United%20States%2C%20European%20powers%20and%20Saudi%20Arabia%20blamed%20Iran%20for%20a%202019%20missile%20and%20drone%20attack%20that%20crippled%20the%20world's%20biggest%20oil%20processing%20facility%20in%20Saudi%20%C2%A0Arabia%2C%20though%20Iran%20denied%20any%20involvement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20U.S.%20president%20Donald%20Trump%20pointed%20to%20Iran's%20missile%20programme%20as%20one%20of%20the%20points%20not%20addressed%20in%20its%202015%20nuclear%20deal%20with%20world%20powers%20and%20cited%20that%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20pulling%20out%20of%20the%20agreement%20in%202018.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Guards%20have%20extensive%20conventional%20combat%20hardware%20and%20capabilities%2C%20which%20were%20showcased%20in%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20conflicts%20in%20Syria%20and%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20IS%20THE%20IRGC'S%20POSITION%20IN%20IRAN'S%20POLITICAL%20SYSTEM%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFormer%20Revolutionary%20Guards%20officers%20occupy%20key%20positions%20in%20Iran's%20establishment%2C%20from%20the%20government%20to%20parliament.%20Most%20of%20President%20Ebrahim%20Raisi's%20cabinet%20are%20former%20IRGC%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IRGC's%20mandate%20to%20protect%20revolutionary%20values%20has%20prompted%20it%20to%20speak%20out%20when%20it%20felt%20the%20system%20was%20threatened.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20ABOUT%20BUSINESS%20INTERESTS%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%201980s%20war%20with%20Iraq%2C%20the%20IRGC%20became%20heavily%20involved%20in%20Iran's%20re