20light%20damage%20to%20one%20Israeli%20military%20facility.%20He%20said%20the%20engagement%20had%20not%20ended%2C%20and%20Israeli%20forces%20were%20still%20intercepting%20incoming%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20Channel%2012%20TV%20cited%20an%20unnamed%20Israeli%20official%20as%20saying%20there%20would%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bsignificant%20response%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIran%20has%20vowed%20retaliation%20for%20what%20it%20called%20an%20Israeli%20strike%20on%20its%20Damascus%20consulate%20on%20April%201%20that%20killed%20seven%20Guards%20officers%20including%20two%20senior%20commanders%20and%20said%20its%20strike%20was%20a%20punishment%20for%20%26quot%3BIsraeli%20crimes%26quot%3B.%20Israel%20has%20neither%20confirmed%20nor%20denied%20responsibility%20for%20the%20consulate%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BShould%20the%20Israeli%20regime%20make%20another%20mistake%2C%20Iran's%20response%20will%20be%20considerably%20more%20severe%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Iranian%20mission%20to%20the%20United%20Nations%20said%2C%20warning%20the%20U.S.%20to%20%26quot%3Bstay%20away%26quot%3B.%20However%2C%20it%20also%20said%20Iran%20now%20%26quot%3Bdeemed%20the%20matter%20concluded%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnited%20Nations%20Secretary-General%20Antonio%20Guterres%20condemned%20Iran's%20attack%2C%20and%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bdeeply%20alarmed%20about%20the%20very%20real%20danger%20of%20a%20devastating%20region-wide%20escalation.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20who%20on%20Friday%20had%20warned%20Iran%20against%20an%20attack%2C%20cut%20short%20a%20visit%20to%20his%20home%20state%20of%20Delaware%20to%20meet%20national%20security%20advisers%20in%20the%20White%20House%20Situation%20Room%2C%20an%20official%20said.%20He%20pledged%20to%20stand%20with%20Israel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20commitment%20to%20Israel's%20security%20against%20threats%20from%20Iran%20and%20its%20proxies%20is%20ironclad%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X%20after%20the%20meeting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Gaza%20war%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%2C%20now%20in%20its%20seventh%20month%2C%20has%20driven%20up%20tensions%20in%20the%20region%2C%20spreading%20to%20fronts%20with%20Lebanon%20and%20Syria%20and%20drawing%20long-range%20fire%20at%20Israeli%20targets%20from%20as%20far%20away%20as%20Yemen%20and%20Iraq.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBritish%20maritime%20security%20company%20Ambrey%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20drones%20were%20also%20reportedly%20launched%20against%20Israel%20by%20Yemen's%20Iran-aligned%20Houthi%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThose%20clashes%20now%20threaten%20to%20morph%20into%20a%20direct%20open%20conflict%20pitting%20Iran%20and%20its%20regional%20allies%20against%20Israel%20and%20its%20main%20supporter%20the%20United%20States%2C%20with%20regional%20power%20Egypt%20urging%20%26quot%3Butmost%20restraint%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Israel%20and%20Iran%20have%20been%20bitter%20foes%20for%20decades%2C%20their%20long%20feud%20has%20mostly%20unfolded%20via%20proxies%20or%20by%20targeting%20each%20other's%20forces%20operating%20in%20third%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20and%20British%20warplanes%20were%20involved%20in%20shooting%20down%20some%20Israel-bound%20drones%20over%20the%20Iraq-Syria%20border%20area%2C%20Channel%2012%20reported.%20Three%20U.S.%20officials%20said%20the%20U.S.%20military%20had%20shot%20down%20drone%20aircraft%20without%20saying%20how%20many.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EESCALATION%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsraeli%20Prime%20Minister%20Benjamin%20Netanyahu%2C%20whose%20official%20jet%20took%20off%20shortly%20after%20the%20attack%20began%2C%20convened%20the%20war%20cabinet%20at%20a%20military%20headquarters%20in%20Tel%20Aviv%2C%20his%20office%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIsrael's%20military%20said%20sirens%20would%20sound%20in%20any%20threatened%20areas%20and%20that%20its%20defences%20were%20poised%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20drones%2C%2