.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20updates%20address%20who%20can%20use%20Disability%20Access%20Services%2C%20among%20other%20changes.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EGuests%20attempting%20to%20misuse%20the%20program%20will%20receive%20a%20lifetime%20ban.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDisney%20has%20updated%20its%20theme%20park%20policies%20for%20guests%20with%20disabilities%20as%20it%20tries%20to%20crack%20down%20on%20those%20misusing%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20policy%20comes%20as%20Disney%20confronts%20a%20rise%20in%20the%20number%20of%20guests%20exploiting%20the%20program.%20A%20spokesperson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-world-florida-third-party-tour-guide-crackdown-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econfirmed%20for%20Business%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20November%202023%20that%20there%20had%20been%20an%20increase%20in%20people%20taking%20advantage%20of%20its%20disability%20policies%20to%20skip%20lines%20and%20avoid%20crowds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDisability%20services%20have%20become%20the%20most%20requested%20service%20at%20the%20Florida%20and%20California%20parks%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.washingtonpost.com%2Ftravel%2F2024%2F04%2F11%2Fdisney-disability-access-service-das%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Washington%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20company%20reported%20that%20use%20of%20the%20services%20has%20more%20than%20tripled%20over%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Visitors%20to%20Mickey's%20Toontown%20ride%20Chip%20n'%20Dale's%20GADGETcoaster%20inside%20Disneyland%20Park%20in%20Anaheim%2C%20CA%2C%20on%20Saturday%2C%20March%2018%2C%202023.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65bd13df43bb77284ba3063c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223248%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDisneyland.%20%3Cp%3EMediaNews%20Group%2FOrange%20County%20Register%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigu