%20housing%20costs.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20those%20with%20the%20lowest%20incomes%20spent%2039%25%20less%20on%20food%20and%2042%25%20less%20on%20healthcare%20than%20their%20%26quot%3Bunburdened%20counterparts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20roadblocks%20to%20Airbnb's%20renter%20initiative%20is%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20the%20early%20laws%20that%20were%20made%20limited%20short-term%20rental%20to%20homeownership%2C%26quot%3B%20Theo%20Yedinsky%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20public%20policy%20at%20Airbnb%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnn.com%2F2024%2F04%2F12%2Ftech%2Fairbnb-renters-homeowners%2Findex.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etold%20CNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20towns%20and%20cities%20across%20North%20America%20have%20begun%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcities-fighting-airbnbs-with-regulations-for-short-term-rentals-2022-5%23burlington-vermont-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecracking%20down%20on%20short-term%20rentals%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20requiring%20licenses%20and%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20asking%20short-term%20rental%20owners%20to%20live%20in%20the%20property%20as%20their%20primary%20residence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20promising%20sign%20%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Efor%20Airbnb%2C%20at%20least%3Cstrong%3E%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20is%20that%20Virginia%20signed%20a%20law%20earlier%20this%20week%20that%20requires%20localities%20that%20issue%20short-term%20rental%20permits%20to%20property%20owners%20to%20issue%20the%20same%20permit%20to%20tenants%20%E2%80%94%20provided%20they%20have%20permission%20from%20the%20property%20owner.%20Cities%20like%20Raleigh%2C%20San%20Diego%2C%20and%20Tulsa%20have%20also%20passed%20%26quot%3Brenter-friendly%26quot%3B%20policies%2C%20Airbnb%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHomeownership%20should%20not%20be%20a%20barrier%20to%20entry%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20sharing%20your%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Mike%20Signer%2C%20Airbnb'