d%20for%20the%20petite%20suite%2C%20as%20it%20was%20the%20least%20expensive%20option%20at%202395%20Danish%20Krone%2C%20or%20around%20%24340%20for%20an%20overnight%20stay%20on%20March%2031.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20suite%20was%2034%20square%20meters%20and%20had%20a%20bedroom%20with%20a%20four-poster%20bed%20(pictured)%20and%20a%20TV%2C%20a%20living%20room%20with%20two%20sofas%20and%20a%20second%20TV%2C%20a%20bathroom%20with%20a%20shower%2C%20and%20a%20coffee%20and%20tea%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20comparison%2C%20the%20classic%20suite%20has%20the%20same%20amenities%20but%20is%20slightly%20larger%20at%2040%20square%20meters%2C%20according%20to%20the%20hotel%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20suite%20overlooked%20the%20jungle%20pool.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Manon%20Les%20Suites%20hotel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66168e6e16bde8d4ead7429f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author's%20partner%20outside%20their%20hotel%20suite.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20has%2087%20suites%20and%20six%20floors.%20Most%20suites%20have%20a%20balcony%20overlooking%20the%20pool%2C%20with%20the%20exception%20of%20the%20pool-side%20suites%2C%20which%20are%20located%20next%20to%20the%20pool%20on%20the%20same%20floor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20warm%20decor%20and%20spacious%20living%20room%20made%20us%20feel%20at%20home.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Copenhagen%20hotel%20lounge%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619052f3f923f7dab072901%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20lounge%20area.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20suite%20was%20spacious%20and%20luxurious%20%E2%80%94%20I%20loved%20that%20we%20each%20had%20a%20sofa%2C%20as%20there%20were%20two%20of%20them.%20We%20were%20also%20impressed%20with%20the%20decor%3A%20The%20cozy%20rug%2C%20throw%20pillows%2C%20and%20an%20abundance%20of%20colorful%20paintings%20made%20it%20feel%20homey.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20tea%20and%20coffee%20station%20had%20a%20kettle%2C%20a%20selection%20of%20tea%2C%20two%20recyclable%20water%20bottles%2C%20a%20fully%20stocked%20mini-fridge%2C%20and%20snacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20were%20impressed%20with%20the%20complimentary%20items%20in%20the%20bathroom.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222040%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Copenhagen%20hotel%20bathroom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6618f1d616bde8d4ead831f1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20bathroom.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bathroom%20had%20tiled%20walls%2C%20a%20large%20mirror%2C%20a%20walk-in%20shower%2C%20and%20a%20cabinet%20containing%20complimentary%20items%2C%20including%20bamboo%20toothbrushes%2C%20toothpaste%20tablets%2C%20crystal%20deodorant%2C%20and%20a%20%26quot%3Bsleep%20kit%26quot%3B%20bag%20that%20had%20an%20eye%20mask%20and%20ear%20plugs%20inside.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20didn't%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20bringing%20our%20own%20robes%20and%20towels%20for%20the%20hotel.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22complimentary%20hotel%20robes%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66192e4d16bde8d4ead83b77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EComplimentary%20robes.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20noticed%20other%20hotel%20guests%20lounging%20around%20in%20matching%20pink%20and%20green%20patterned%20robes.%20Those%20same%20robes%20were%20waiting%20for%20us%20in%20our%20suite%2C%20alongside%20a%20selection%20of%20towels.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20spent%20most%20of%20our%20time%20at%20the%20pool.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221820%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22jungle%20pool%20hotel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661906261caec1275a6f6896%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Bali-inspired%20jungle%20pool%20at%20Manon%20Les%20Suites.%3Cp%3EManon%20Les%20Suites%20Press%20Library%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20getting%20into%20our%20swimwear%20and%20robes%2C%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20made%20our%20way%20to%20the%20jungle%20pool%2C%20which%20had%20free%20deck%20chairs%20and%20a%20bar%20where%20guests%20could%20order%20food%20and%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20hotel%20also%20had%20a%20rooftop%20spa%2C%20a%20sauna%2C%20and%20a%20gym%2C%20which%20we%20didn't%20use%20since%20we%20were%20only%20there%20for%20one%20night.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20leafy%20foliage%20was%20just%20as%20magnificent%20in%20real%20life.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20jungle%20pool%20at%20Manon%20Les%20Suites%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66192fa816bde8d4ead83bf5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20jungle%20pool%20at%20Manon%20Les%20Suites.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20wondered%20if%20our%20time%20at%20the%20hotel%20would%20live%20up%20to%20my%20expectations%2C%20and%20in%20my%20opinion%2C%20it%20was%20even%20better.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dangling%20leafy%20foliage%20was%20absolutely%20stunning%2C%20and%20I%20found%20myself%20constantly%20looking%20up%20in%20awe.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20pool%20was%20heated%2C%20and%20relaxing%20music%20played%20from%20speakers.%20After%20ordering%20drinks%20at%20the%20bar%2C%20we%20were%20pleasantly%20surprised%20when%20a%20staff%20member%20said%20they%20would%20be%20delivered%20to%20our%20deck%20chairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20hotel%20has%20a%20rooftop%20bar%20and%20restaurant%2C%20which%20is%20open%20to%20non-hotel%20guests.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221482%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20server%20pours%20wine%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6619431b3f923f7dab073c8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221112%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20server%20pours%20at%20Restaurant%20Chapung%20in%20Manon%20Les%20Suites.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EChapung%20is%20an%20asian%20fusion%20restaurant%20and%20bar%20on%20the%20hotel's%20sixth%20floor.%20We%20visited%20the%20restaurant%20for%20dinner%20a%20couple%20of%20nights%20before%20our%20stay%2C%20as%20we%20had%20read%20that%20only%20%26quot%3Blunch%20and%20snacks%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20available%20to%20order%20on%20Sunday%2C%20the%20day%20we%20checked%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20we%20waited%20to%20be%20seated%20at%20the%20restaurant%2C%20my%20partner%20ordered%20a%20glass%20of%20wine%20while%20I%20ordered%20a%20cocktail%20from%20the%20bar.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20space%20was%20dimly%20lit%2C%20giving%20it%20a%20romantic%20feel.%20The%20bar%20had%20comfortable%20couches%20with%20throw%20pillows%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20was%20a%20nice%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOur%20%2486%20meal%20was%20delicious%2C%20but%20I%20thought%20the%20portions%20were%20a%20tad%20small.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chapung%20restaurant%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661943753f923f7dab073cff%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EOur%20food%20at%20Chapung.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20the%20sweet%20and%20sour%20salmon%2C%20which%20cost%20%3Cspan%3E165%20Danish%20Krone%20(around%20%2423)%20with%20jasmine%20rice%2C%20which%20cost%2045%20Danish%20krone%20(around%20%246.40).%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20partner%20had%20the%20grilled%20ribeye%20steak%2C%20which%20cost%20310%20Danish%20Krone%20(around%20%2444)%20with%20a%20side%20of%20fries%2C%20which%20cost%2095%20Danish%20Krone%20(around%20%2413).%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20food%20was%20delicious%2C%20but%20we%20thought%20the%20portion%20sizes%20could%20have%20been%20a%20tad%20bigger%20considering%20the%20meal%20was%20(unsurprisingly)%20expensive.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20hotel%20was%20a%20highlight%20of%20our%20trip%2C%20and%20we'd%20willingly%20spend%20another%20%24340%20to%20go%20back.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mikhaila%20and%20scott%20copenhagen%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66191c9916bde8d4ead838bf%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMikhaila%20and%20her%20partner%20in%20Copenhagen%2C%20Denmark.%3Cp%3EMikhaila%20Friel%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20era%20where%20luxury%20travel%20is%20becoming%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F04%2F01%2Fwhy-is-luxury-travel-so-expensive-high-prices-arent-curbing-demand.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emore%20expensive%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20can%20be%20hard%20to%20decide%20where%20to%20put%20your%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELuxury%20hotels%20are%20having%20a%20moment%2C%20with%20prices%20expected%20to%20reach%20%26quot%3Bpeak%20levels%26quot%3B%20in%202024.%20Daily%20rates%20are%20going%20to%20cost%2070%25%20more%20than%20in%202019%2C%20a%20representative%20for%20the%20luxury%20travel%20company%20Virtuoso%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2024%2F04%2F01%2Fwhy-is-luxury-travel-so-expensive-high-prices-arent-curbing-demand.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ECNBC%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EExperts%20told%20the%20outlet%20that%20economic%20uncertainty%20caused%20by%20the%20rising%20cost%20of%20living%20and%20inflation%20won't%20have%20an%20impact%20on%20the%20