k%20it%20was%20my%20father%20who%20saved%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20Dean%20said%20in%202002%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%20%26quot%3BSo%20many%20other%20people%20thought%20the%20Titanic%20would%20never%20sink%2C%20and%20they%20didn't%20bother.%20My%20father%20didn't%20take%20a%20chance.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDean%2C%20her%20mother%2C%20and%20brother%20were%20put%20on%20lifeboat%2013%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Fnews.bbc.co.uk%2F2%2Fhi%2Fuk_news%2F1928026.stm%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBBC%20News.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20survivors%20on%20lifeboats%20were%20later%20picked%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-titanic-passengers-getting-rescued-by-carpathia-2020-4%5C%22%3Eby%20the%20RMS%20Carpathia%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20taken%20to%20New%20York%20City.%20But%20Dean's%20father%20was%20among%20the%20more%20than%201%2C500%20people%20who%20died%20in%20the%20tragedy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDean%20said%20she%20believed%20it%20was%20true%20that%20White%20Star%20Lines%20employees%20had%20prevented%20third-class%20passengers%20from%20going%20above%20deck%20and%20potentially%20escaping%20the%20sinking%20ship%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20couldn't%20happen%20nowadays%2C%20and%20it's%20so%20wrong%2C%20so%20unjust.%20What%20do%20they%20say%3F%20'Judy%20O'Grady%20and%20the%20colonel's%20lady%20are%20sisters%20under%20the%20skin.'%20That's%20the%20way%20it%20should%20have%20been%20that%20night%2C%20but%20it%20wasn't%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWhen%20the%20Deans%20returned%20to%20England%20aboard%20the%20Adriatic%2C%20passengers%20lined%20up%20to%20hold%20the%20baby.%20The%20demand%20was%20so%20high%20an%20officer%20made%20a%20rule%20that%20each%20person%20could%20only%20hold%20her%20for%2010%20minutes.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224362%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20happy%20family%20can%20