use%20it%20was%20her%20husband%20and%20they%20were%20only%20married%20four%20years.%20He%20was%20strikingly%20handsome.%20I%20didn't%20know%20anything%20about%20it%20until%20I%20was%208%20years%20old.%20And%20then%20my%20mother%20got%20married%20again.%20That's%20when%20I%20first%20heard%20about%20the%20Titanic%2C%20and%20about%20my%20father%20going%20down%2C%20everything%20like%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.belfasttelegraph.co.uk%2Flife%2Ffeatures%2Frediscovered-after-years-in-a-desk-final-interview-with-the-last-survivor-of-the-titanic%2F34648089.html%5C%22%3EBelfast%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20interview%20with%20the%20Irish%20Times%2C%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times%20reported%2C%20Dean%20said%20that%20her%20mother%20suffered%20severe%20headaches%20every%20day%20after%20the%20sinking.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EMillvina%20and%20Bertram%20Dean%20were%20educated%20using%20money%20from%20the%20Titanic%20Relief%20Fund%2C%20a%20charity%20formed%20in%20England%20to%20support%20survivors.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Titanic%20survivor%20Millvina%20Dean%2C%20who%20was%20nine%20weeks%20old%20when%20the%20ship%20went%20down%2C%20standing%20by%20street%20named%20for%20her.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e2df5e96242f0019e7e084%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22999%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMillvina%20Dean%20and%20a%20street%20that%20was%20named%20after%20her.%3Cp%3EIan%20Cook%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20Star%20Line%20rather%20infamously%20didn't%20accept%20any%20liability%20for%20the%20Titanic's%20sinking%20for%20years%2C%20even%20though%20the%20tragedy%20left%20almost%20all%20of%20its%20passengers%20with%20no%20money%2C%20no%20possessions%2C%20and%20in%20many%20cases%2C%20no%20breadwinner%20%E2%80%94%20many%20families%20lost%20their%20husbands%20and%20fathers%20since%20they%20couldn't%20get%20on%20lifeboats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wsj.com%2Farticles%2FSB1044398577689669693%5C%22%3EThe%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20in%202003%20that%20four%20years%20after%20the%20crash%2C%20the%20White%20Star%20Line%20agreed%20to%20pay%20the%20US%20%24665%2C000%2C%20or%20roughly%20%24430%20per%20passenger.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20that'd%20be%20around%20%2412%2C700%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDuring%20World%20War%20II%2C%20she%20worked%20in%20the%20British%20Army's%20map-making%20office.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222806%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Map%20showing%20the%20deadlock%20between%20the%20Allied%20and%20German%20forces%20along%20the%20Yser%20canal%2C%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e2e3c596242f0019e7e131%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222104%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20World%20War%20II-era%20map.%3Cp%3ECulture%20Club%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20war%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20secretary%20in%20an%20engineering%20office%20for%2020%20years%2C%20reported%20the%20Los%20Angeles%20Times.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EShe%20never%20publicly%20spoke%20about%20the%20Titanic%20until%201985%2C%20when%20the%20shipwreck%20was%20found.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22mellvina%20dean%20in%202002%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e2dd8b27e5db0018eea6c1%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222625%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMillvina%20Dean%20at%20another%20Titanic%20exhibition.%3Cp%3EGERRY%20PENNY%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNobody%20knew%20about%20me%20and%20the%20Titanic%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20nobody%20took%20any%20interest%2C%20so%20I%20took%20no%20interest%20either%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20according%20to%20The%20New%20York%20Times.%20%26quot%3BBut%20then%20they%20found%20the%20wreck%2C%20and%20after%20they%20found%20the%20wreck%2C%20they%20found%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20decades%20after%2C%20Millvina%20Dean%20attended%20many%20Titanic%20exhibitions%2C%20conventions%2C%20and%20events.%20She%20also%20traveled%20to%20different%20schools%20to%20tell%20her%20life's%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EDean%20never%20watched%20James%20Cameron's%201997%20blockbuster%20%26quot%3BTitanic%26quot%3B%20because%20she%20was%20worried%20it%20would%20make%20her%20think%20about%20what%20her%20father%20had%20been%20doing%20in%20his%20final%20moments.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22titanic%20movie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F63e2dda696242f0019e7e04f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221201%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%26quot%3BTitanic.%26quot%3B%3Cp%3EIMDb%2F20th%20Century%20Fox%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20Dean%20had%20said%20she%20didn't%20feel%20a%20huge%20connection%20to%20her%20father%2C%20since%20she%20never%20really%20knew%20him%2C%20she%20couldn't%20watch%20any%20movies%20or%20documentaries%20relating%20to%20the%20Titanic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBecause%20that's%20the%20ship%20on%20which%20my%20father%20went%20down.%20Although%20I%20didn't%20remember%20him%2C%20nothing%20about%20him%2C%20I%20would%20still%20be%20emotional.%20I%20would%20think%3A%20'How%20did%20he%20go%20down%3F%20Did%20he%20go%20down%20with%20the%20ship%20or%20did%20he%20jump%20overboard%3F'%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20the%20Belfast%20Telegraph%20in%20May%202009%2C%20weeks%20before%20her%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHer%20brother%20Bertram%2C%20pictured%20right%2C%20died%20on%20the%2080th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20iceberg%20collision%20in%201992.%20He%20was%2081.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222782%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22American%20scientist%20Dr%20Robert%20Ballard%20(centre)%2C%20who%20led%20last%20year's%20deep%20sea%2