9COne%20can%20never%20have%20enough%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F330111%2Ftanya-abraham-journalist-writes-eating-with-history-kerala-food-recipes-history%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebooks%20around%20heritage%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20smiles%20Johann.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20anyone%20who%20would%20like%20to%20know%20what%E2%80%99s%20in%20those%20books%20%E2%80%94%20the%20secrets%20of%20South%20India%20and%20first-hand%20stories%20of%20the%20lores%20surrounding%20Fort%20Kochi%20%E2%80%94%20there%20are%20two%20ways.%20Either%20you%20ask%20Johann%20to%20share%20his%20reading%20list%20or%20you%20attend%20one%20of%20the%20many%20experiential%20walks%20organised%20by%20him%20and%20his%20team%20as%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98Kochi%20Heritage%20Project%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Not%20shy%20of%20my%20heritage.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0000-1712923055.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Johann's%20heritage%20walks%20across%20Kochi's%20bazaars%2C%20forts%2C%20quaint%20streets%20and%20iconic%20spots%20are%20loved%20by%20people%20of%20all%20ages%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0000-1712923055.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0000-1712923055-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0000-1712923055-500x282.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FIMG-20240412-WA0000-1712923055-768x433.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F0