3ERedefining%20the%20wheelchair%20experience%20with%20its%20user-centric%20design%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20heading%20R2D2%2C%20Prof%20Srinivasan%20also%20teaches%20at%20the%20Department%20of%20Mechanical%20Engineering%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F337953%2Fiit-madras-free-online-course-for-engineers-on-data-science-certificate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT%20Madras%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Articulating%20the%20vision%20of%20this%20project%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIntegrating%20standing%20function%20in%20a%20wheelchair%20provides%20health%20benefits%20as%20well%20as%20functional%20and%20psychological%20benefits%20to%20the%20user.%20Our%20first%20standing%20wheelchair%20was%20Arise%2C%20a%20low-cost%20mechanical%20design%2C%20specially%20designed%20for%20rural%20users%2C%20enabling%20standing%20and%20outdoor%20mobility%20for%20short%20distances.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20compact%20standing%20wheelchair%20with%20an%20easy-to-use%20actuation%20system%20makes%20everyday%20activities%20%E2%80%94%20like%20engaging%20in%20eye-level%20conversations%2C%20reaching%20for%20a%20book%20or%20enjoying%20a%20meal%20standing%20by%20a%20counter%20%E2%80%94%20much%20easier%20for%20wheelchair%20users%2C%20and%20also%20provides%20real%20health%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20most%20wheelchair%20users%20in%20India%2C%20the%20ability%20to%20stand%20is%20a%20real%20luxury.%20But%20standing%20is%20essential%20for%20better%20blood%20circulation%2C%20digestion%2C%20preventing%20pressure%20sores%2C%20etc.%20Besides%20physical%20health%2C%20there%20is%20also%20a%20real%20mental%20health%20and%20economic%20element%20to%20standing%20for%20wheelchair%20users.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20this%20November%202013%20academic%20paper%20published%20in%20Physiotherapy%20Canada%2C%20%E2%80%9CProlonged%20standing%20has%20been%20shown%20to%20have%20beneficial%20effects%20on%20various%20body%20functions%20and%20structures.%20In%20addition%2C%20time%20spent%20in%20a%20standing%20position%20can%20give%20wheelchair%20users%20a%20sense%20of%20confidence%20and%20equality%20through%20face-to-face%20contact%20with%20the%20non-disabled%20community.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20a%20standing%20device%20can%20provide%20opportunities%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20outside%20world%2C%20enhance%20memories%20from%20the%20past%2C%20and%20promote%20hope%20for%20the%20future%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustin%20Jesudas%20%E2%80%94%20head%20of%20operations%20at%20R2D2%20with%2014%20years%20of%20lived%20experience%20as%20a%20tetraplegic%20and%20an%20elite%20para-athlete%20%E2%80%94%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWheelchairs%20enable%20us%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20safe%20space%20for%20our%20mobility%20and%20to%20perform%20daily%20activities.%20The%20ability%20to%20stand%20with%20just%20a%20push%20of%20a%20button%20makes%20the%20wheelchair%20even%20more%20inclusive%2C%20helping%20tetraplegics%20to%20stand%20independently.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20wheelchair%20users%20are%20often%20dependent%20on%20external%20help%20and%20some%20need%20to%20use%20orthoses%20to%20stand.%20For%20users%20with%20compromised%20upper%20body%20strength%2C%20this%20is%20a%20significant%20challenge%2C%20and%20a%20manual%20standing%20wheelchair%20is%20inadequate%2C%20notes%20the%20press%20release%20issued%20by%20IIT-Madras.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20why%20in%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20Professor%20Sujatha%20Srinivasan%20recalls%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20idea%20for%20NeoStand%20was%20fueled%20by%20encounters%20with%20individuals%20who%2C%20despite%20their%20desire%20for%20independence%2C%20found%20themselves%20reliant%20on%20others%20due%20to%20their%20physical%20limitations.%20The%20journey%20to%20developing%20NeoStand%20began%20in%20August%202021%20with%20our%20observation%20that%20users%20of%20the%20Arise%20Standing%20Wheelchair%2C%20despite%20its%20innovations%2C%20were%20limited%20by%20the%20requirement%20for%20upper%20body%20strength%20to%20operate%20the%20arm%20and%20hand-powered%20standing%20function.%20This%20limitation%20sparked%20our%20determination%20to%20design%20a%20solution%20that%20could%20bridge%20this%20gap.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNeoStand%2C%20with%20its%20electric%20standing%20function%2C%20was%20conceived%20to%20empower%20a%20broader%20spectrum%20of%20users%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20lacking%20the%20upper%20body%20strength%20for%20manual%20operation%20%E2%80%94%20and%20to%20facilitate%20caregivers%20in%20providing%20support%20with%20less%20physical%20strain.%20Its%20compact%20design%20further%20addresses%20the%20need%20for%20a%20practical%2C%20space-efficient%20solution%20in%20urban%20environments%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20putting%20less%20strain%20on%20the%20shoulders%20of%20caregivers%20or%20therapists%20in%20the%20hospital%2C%20the%20NeoStand%20also%20carries%20importance%20from%20a%20therapeutic%20standpoint.%20Caregivers%20or%20therapists%20can%20help%20the%20user%20practise%20standing%20gradually%20since%20NeoStand%20allows%20the%20user%20to%20stop%20at%20intermediate%20positions.%20This%20is%20very%20useful%20from%20a%20therapeutic%20standpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EElaborating%20further%2C%20she%20describes%20how%20it%20promises%20users%20the%20freedom%20to%20sit%20for%20prolonged%20hours%20and%20stand%20comfortably%20when%20needed%2C%20reducing%20the%20risk%20of%20secondary%20health%20complications.%20%E2%80%9CIts%20compactness%20ensures%20easy%20manoeuvrability%20through%20tight%20spaces%2C%20enhancing%20accessibility.%20The%20seamless%20transition%20between%20sitting%20and%20standing%2C%20with%20an%20option%20to%20pause%20midway%2C%20underscores%20its%20innovative%20approach%20to%20improving%20users%E2%80%99%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20social%20participation%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20610px)%20100vw%2C%20610px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-4-1712752478.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22610%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Electric%20Standing%20Wheelchair%20developed%20by%20IIT-Madras%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-4-1712752478.jpg%20610w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-4-1712752478-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-4-1712752478-500x751.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-4-1712752478-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346988%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22916%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ENeoStand%20developed%20for%20disabled%20persons%20by%20IIT%20Madras-incubated%20NeoMotion%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDeveloping%20the%20NeoStand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20stated%20earlier%2C%20the%20conceptualisation%20of%20NeoStand%20took%20root%20in%20August%202021%20driven%20by%20a%20clear%20vision%20to%20enhance%20mobility%20solutions.%20As%20Professor%20Sujatha%20recalls%20speaking%20to%3Cstrong%3E%20The%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20development%20process%20was%20marked%20by%20rigorous%20testing%20and%20refinement%2C%20with%20our%20team%20completing%20four%20design%20iterations%20to%20perfect%20the%20NeoStand.%20This%20iterative%20process%20was%20crucial%20in%20evolving%20the%20prototype%20into%20the%20market-ready%20product%20we%20are%20proud%20to%20introduce%20today.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20developing%20the%20NeoStand%20did%20pose%20challenges%2C%20particularly%20in%20achieving%20a%20sleek%2C%20compact%20design%20suitable%20for%20indoor%20use%20without%20compromising%20on%20smooth%20propulsion%20and%20functionality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20team%20tackled%20these%20challenges%20through%20a%20blend%20of%20systematic%20engineering%20and%20thoughtful%20industrial%20design%2C%20ensuring%20that%20the%20final%20product%20not%20only%20met%20but%20exceeded%20our%20objectives.%20This%20process%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20our%20dedication%20to%20innovation%20and%20our%20relentless%20pursuit%20of%20solutions%20that%20enhance%20the%20quality%20of%20life%20for%20our%20users%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EUnderstanding%20NeoStand%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeoStand%20is%20engineered%20with%20four%20key%20systems%3A%20the%20seating%20system%20for%20comfort%2C%20the%20manual%20propulsion%20system%20for%20mobility%2C%20the%20electric%20standing%20system%20for%20effortless%20transition%20from%20sitting%20to%20standing%2C%20and%20the%20safety%20system%20to%20ensure%20secure%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20seating%20system%20offers%20tailored%20adjustments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20seat%20width%2C%20depth%2C%20and%20backrest%20height%2C%20for%20prolonged%20comfort.%20The%20manual%20propulsion%20is%20enhanced%20by%20ergonomic%20design%20elements%2C%20facilitating%20smoother%20mobility.%20The%20electric%20standing%20system%20employs%20a%20battery-powered%20actuator%20to%20smoothly%20transition%20the%20user%20to%20an%20upright%20position%2C%20while%20the%20safety%20system%20includes%20features%20like%20wheel%20locks%20and%20chest%20harnesses%20for%20added%20stability%20and%20security%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Swostik%20Sourav%20Dash%2C%20Co-Founder%20and%20CEO%20at%20NeoMotion%2C%20speaking%20to%20The%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPowering%20the%20NeoStand%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269173%2Fjudy-jeevaranjan-nasa-scientist-ul-women-inspiration-innovation-lithium-ion-battery%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELithium-ion%20battery%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20chosen%20for%20its%20reliability%20and%20performance.%20This%20battery%20enables%20users%20to%20seamlessly%20transition%20between%20seated%20and%20upright%20positions%20up%20to%20200%20times%20on%20a%20single%20charge.%20Furthermore%2C%20the%20battery%E2%80%99s%20quick%20recharge%20capability%20%E2%80%94%20fully%20recharging%20within%20just%20four%20hours%20%E2%80%94%20ensures%20minimal%20downtime%2C%20enhancing%20the%20user%20experience%20by%20providing%20consistent%20support%20throughout%20the%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Professor%20Sujatha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriced%20at%20Rs%2089%2C900%2C%20the%20NeoStand%20is%20positioned%20to%20make%20advanced%20mobility%20solutions%20more%20accessible%2C%20argues%20Swostik.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20currently%20available%20for%20purchase%20directly%20through%20NeoMotion%2C%20with%20contact%20details%20provided%20on%20their%20website%20for%20ease%20of%20access.%20Our%20commitment%20to%20affordability%20extends%20beyond%20the%20price%20tag%2C%20as%20we%20explore%20various%20strategies%20to%20make%20devices%20like%20the%20NeoStand%20more%20accessible%20to%20wider%20communities%2C%20ensuring%20that%20advanced%20mobility%20solutions%20reach%20those%20who%20need%20them%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20elaborates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201375px)%20100vw%2C%201375px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-3-1712752549.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221375%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22electric%20standing%20wheelchair%20called%20NeoStand%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStand-IIT-Madras-3-1712752549.jpg%201375w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FNeoStan