hip%20model%20extends%20beyond%20financial%20grants%2C%20aiming%20to%20encompass%20support%20for%20the%20extensive%20R%26amp%3BD%20work%20conducted%20at%20R2D2%2C%20as%20well%20as%20backing%20for%20the%20initiatives%20undertaken%20by%20the%20National%20Center%20for%20Assistive%20Health%20Technologies%20at%20IIT%20Madras%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20forward%2C%20Professor%20Sujatha%20speaks%20of%20the%20%E2%80%9Cpressing%20need%E2%80%9D%20they%E2%80%99re%20addressing%20%E2%80%94%20the%20provision%20of%20an%20adapted%20bus%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20service%20is%20crucial%20for%20transporting%20persons%20with%20disabilities%20to%20and%20from%20our%20centres%2C%20especially%20during%20the%20sports%20and%20cultural%20events%20we%20organise.%20Given%20the%20lack%20of%20accessible%20public%20transportation%20options%20in%20our%20cities%2C%20this%20initiative%20represents%20a%20vital%20link%20in%20ensuring%20participation%20and%20accessibility%20for%20all%20attendees.%20This%20kind%20of%20%5Bcorporate%5D%20support%20goes%20a%20long%20way%20in%20amplifying%20the%20impact%20of%20our%20work%20and%20underscores%20the%20multifaceted%20nature%20of%20the%20assistance%20we%20seek%20from%20our%20partners%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fr2d2.iitm.ac.in%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIIT-Madras%3C%2Fa%3E)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1712835705000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D346982%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20Arise%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20manual%20standing%20wheelchair%2C%20and%20NeoBolt%2C%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20motorised%20add-on%20for%20wheelchairs%2C%20IIT-Madras%20now%20develops%20the%20NeoStand%2C%20an%20indigenously%20developed%20and%20customisable%20electric%