d%20Deachen%20out.%20The%20next%20month%2C%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%207%2C000%20made%20its%20way%20to%20her.%20The%20money%20was%20a%20reimbursement%20for%20the%20cow%20she%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310452%2Fbengaluru-student-financial-independence-portal-for-domestic-workers-finwin-anaya-jethanandani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einsurance%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Mr%20Namgail%20has%20started%20is%20very%20helpful%20to%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20Tsewang%20Norboo%2C%20Deachen%E2%80%99s%20brother-in-law%20shares.%20He%20has%20been%20helping%20her%20out%20following%20the%20death%20of%20her%20husband.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20scheme%2C%20every%20village%20home%20pays%20an%20annual%20sum%20of%20Rs%20400.%20The%20cumulative%20amount%20goes%20into%20the%20bank%20account%20that%20Namgail%20has%20set%20up.%20When%20a%20villager%20reports%20an%20incident%20of%20a%20missing%20cow%20or%20goat%2C%20citing%20the%20snow%20leopard%20as%20the%20culprit%2C%20they%20are%20compensated%20with%20Rs%205%2C000%20(for%20a%20small%20animal)%20and%20Rs%207%2C000%20(for%20a%20larger%20animal).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENamgail%20took%20over%20as%20director%20in%202013%2C%20after%20the%20passing%20away%20of%20his%20beloved%20friend%20and%20mentor%20Rinchen%20Wangchuk.%20The%20Ladakhi%20mountaineer%20and%20conservationist%20had%20co-founded%20the%20trust%20in%202003%20along%20with%20biologist%20Rodney%20Jackson%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20prioritising%20a%20harmonious%20relationship%20between%20the%20snow%20leopard%20and%20the%20locals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20return%20to%20the%20place%20he%20once%20called%20home%20is%20special%20for%20Namgail%20who%20was%20previously%20working%20as%20a%20wildlife%20biologist%20in%20the%20United%20States%20where%20he%20was%20studying%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebette