thebetterindia.com%2F28377%2Fendangered-species-snow-leopard-spotted-in-the-kumaon-himalayas%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20the%20snow%20leopard%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20for%20centuries%20assumed%20a%20%E2%80%98king%E2%80%99%20status%20in%20the%20mountains%20of%20Afghanistan%2C%20Bhutan%2C%20China%2C%20India%2C%20and%20Nepal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20interesting%20to%20note%20is%20that%20the%20snow%20leopard%E2%80%99s%20status%20was%20assessed%20in%201986%2C%201988%2C%201990%2C%201994%2C%201996%2C%202002%2C%20and%202008.%20In%20each%20case%2C%20it%20was%20classified%20as%20%E2%80%98Endangered%E2%80%99.%20But%20in%202008%20the%20animals%E2%80%99%20status%20was%20changed%20to%20%E2%80%98Vulnerable%E2%80%99%20as%20the%20population%20began%20to%20decline%20less%20rapidly.%20But%20the%20decline%20was%20still%20present%2C%20and%20human-animal%20conflict%20was%20to%20blame.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-6-1711367766.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Retaliatory%20killings%20of%20the%20snow%20leopard%20used%20to%20be%20very%20common%20in%20Ladakh%20pushing%20the%20animal%20to%20the%20brink%20of%20extinction%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-6-1711367766.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-6-1711367766-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-6-1711367766-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-6-1711367766-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F03%2Fsnow-leopard-conservancy-6-171136776