e%20uses%20the%20bone%20as%20a%20conductor%20of%20sound.%20The%20device%2C%20placed%20on%20the%20temporal%20bone%2C%20sends%20vibrations%20to%20the%20cochlea.%20It%20bypasses%20the%20physical%20ear%20system%2C%20namely%20the%20outer%20ear%2C%20inner%20ear%20and%20middle%20ear%2C%20directly%20simulating%20the%20last%20part%20of%20the%20ear%2C%20which%20is%20connected%20to%20the%20brain%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Kanishk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20band%2C%20which%20the%20user%20wears%20on%20the%20hand%2C%20is%20equipped%20with%20microprocessors.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20captures%20the%20audio%20and%20sounds%2C%20tunes%20them%2C%20processes%20them%20and%20sends%20them%20to%20the%20hearing%20device%2C%20enabling%20the%20user%20to%20hear.%20The%20Bluetooth%20can%20also%20be%20connected%20to%20any%20other%20device%20like%20a%20mobile%20phone%2C%20TV%2C%20or%20laptop%2C%20helping%20children%20listen%20to%20classes%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20solution%20for%20people%20with%20conductive%20hearing%20loss%20is%20usually%20a%20surgical%20implant%20called%20the%20BAHA%20implant%20(Bone-Anchored%20Hearing%20Aid)%2C%20which%20uses%20the%20same%20technology%20used%20in%20this%20hearing%20aid.%20The%20corresponding%20surgery%20generally%20costs%20Rs%208%20lakh%2C%20according%20to%20the%20founders%2C%20while%20this%20device%20costs%20Rs%2080%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20differentiator%20and%20patent%20is%20for%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20have%20been%20able%20to%20use%20this%20technology%2C%20which%20is%20used%20in%20the%20surgery%20and%20military%20devices%2C%20for%20a%20non-surgical%20hearing%20aid%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20partnered%20with%20the%20All%20India%20Institute%20Of%20Speech%20and%20Hearing%20in%20Mysuru%20for%20clinical%20trials%20and%20also%20received%20grants%20from%20the%20Union%20Government%20and%20State%20Government%20worth%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20to%20fund%20their%20research.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20through%20this%20venture%2C%20the%20duo%20have%20provided%20the%20gift%20of%20hearing%20to%20over%2011%2C500%20children%20and%20adults%20across%20the%20country%20%E2%80%94%20the%20majority%20of%20which%20are%20through%20partnerships%20with%20corporations%20and%20CSR%20activities.%20They%20also%20partner%20with%20State%20Governments%20to%20distribute%20hearing%20aids%20as%20part%20of%20the%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Samagra%20Shiksha%20Abhiyan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20HearNU%20is%20currently%20being%20exported%20to%20countries%20in%20Africa%2C%20with%20plans%20for%20global%20expansion%20supported%20by%20a%20granted%20patent%20covering%2027%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Over%2011%2C500%20devices%20have%20been%20sold%20so%20far%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333-500x374.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333-768x575.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-04-04-at-5.19.10-PM-1712584333-150x112.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-346841%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22958%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EOver%2011%2C500%20devices%20have%20been%20sold%20so%20far%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20success%20of%20HearNU%2C%20they%20also%20launched%20a%20bone%20conduction%20earphone%20called%20WeHear%20OX%2C%20which%20they%20claim%20is%20%E2%80%9Csafe%20for%20our%20ears%E2%80%9D%20as%20it%20bypasses%20the%20physical%20ears%20and%20comes%20equipped%20with%20a%2072-language%20translator.%20These%20earphones%20are%20priced%20at%20Rs%2010%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20working%20on%20HearNU%20BTE%20%E2%80%94%20a%20hearing%20aid%20for%20people%20with%20other%20forms%20of%20hearing%20loss%20%E2%80%94%20and%20have%20three%20more%20products%20in%20the%20pipeline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20want%20to%20create%20an%20ecosystem%20in%20hearing%20aids%20that%20are%20completely%20made%20from%20scratch%20in%20India%2C%20for%20the%20world.%20Our%20solutions%20will%20be%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F250601%2Faarti-rastogi-bengaluru-food-startup-artinci-healthy-sugar-free-keto-friendly-gluten-free-desserts-ice-cream-brownies-cakes-hearing-disability-woman-entrepreneur-him16%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eaffordable%20for%20all%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20ensuring%20that%20everyone%20with%20hearing%20loss%20can%20find%20a%20non-surgical%20alternative%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Kanishka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20WHO%20estimating%20that%20one%20in%2010%20people%20will%20have%20disabling%20hearing%20loss%20by%202050%2C%20such%20solutions%20are%20definitely%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%20WeHear%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.who.int%2Fnews-room%2Ffact-sheets%2Fdetail%2Fdeafness-and-hearing-loss%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EWHO%20Report%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22pub