dwater%2C%20there%20are%20%5Bwater%20scarcity%5D%20problems%20in%20pockets.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%20the%20Bangalore%20Water%20Supply%20and%20Sewerage%20Board%20(BWSSB)%20issued%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.downtoearth.org.in%2Fnews%2Fwater%2Fbengaluru-water-crisis-bwssb-announces-20-water-cut-to-bulk-consumers-identifies-areas-bearing-the-brunt-94973%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20detailed%20list%20%3C%2Fa%3Emarking%20out%20areas%20most%20severely%20impacted%20by%20water%20scarcity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20data%20gathered%20from%20the%20Karnataka%20Groundwater%20Authority%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fcities%2Fbangalore%2Fbengaluru-east-taluk-worst-affected-in-depleting-groundwater-levels-this-summer%2Farticle68002688.ece%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%2029%20March%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20data%20of%20groundwater%20levels%20for%20last%20December%20and%20this%20January%20and%20February%20shows%20that%20Bengaluru%20East%20taluk%2C%20which%20houses%20one%20of%20the%20major%20IT%20corridors%20of%20the%20city%2C%20where%20the%20water%20crisis%20is%20most%20severe%20and%20groundwater%20exploitation%20unbridled%2C%20has%20seen%20the%20most%20dip%20in%20groundwater%20levels%20this%20summer.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESo%2C%20why%20are%20some%20parts%20of%20the%20city%20struggling%20so%20much%20with%20water%20scarcity%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVishwanath%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20the%20perfect%20storm.%20What%20happened%20was%20that%20we%20were%20supposed%20to%20get%20water%20from%20the%20Cauvery%20Phase-5%20project%20(delivering%20775%20million%20litres%20a%20day)%2C%20and%20that%20should%20have%20been%20completed%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20ago.%20If%20this%20project%20had%20been%20completed%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20no%20crisis.%20With%20the%20completion%20of%20this%20project%2C%20millions%20of%20people%20in%20Bengaluru%20who%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20piped%20connection%20would%20have%20one%20with%20water%20flowing%20in%20it.%20But%20that%20project%20got%20delayed%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20be%20completed%20in%20May-June%202024.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAlso%2C%20some%20of%20the%20major%20city%20lakes%20have%20been%20drained%20and%20de-silted.%20That%20project%20should%20have%20been%20completed%20three%20years%20back%2C%20but%20this%20project%20has%20been%20going%20on%20for%20four%20to%20five%20years.%20If%20you%20desilt%20and%20drain%20lakes%20for%20these%20many%20years%2C%20their%20capacity%20to%20recharge%20aquifers%20is%20non-existent.%20That%E2%80%99s%20where%20all%20the%20borewells%20have%20dried%20up%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20parts%20of%20the%20city%2C%20however%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20is%20high%2C%20according%20to%20Vishwanath.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFor%20example%2C%20in%20Cubbon%20Park%2C%20the%20open%20recharge%20wells%20have%20sufficient%20water.%20Some%20of%20the%20lakes%2C%20which%20are%20full%20of%20water%2C%20are%20good%20for%20percolation.%20In%20these%20areas%2C%20the%20borewells%20are%20at%20a%20depth%20of%20150%20to%20300%20feet.%20Where%20there%20is%20no%20piped%20water%20supply%2C%20the%20groundwater%20table%20is%20very%20low.%20If%20the%20Cauvery%20Phase-5%20project%20is%20completed%2C%20the%20problem%20of%20water%20scarcity%20in%20the%20city%20will%20go%20away%20to%20a%20large%20extent.%20If%20the%20lakes%20are%20filled%20with%20rainwater%20or%20tertiary%20treated%20wastewater%2C%20then%20the%20aquifers%20will%20be%20recharged%20and%20the%20problem%20will%20become%20a%20lot%20less%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vishwanath%20noted%20earlier%2C%20there%20are%20real%20problems%20that%20need%20to%20be%20solved%20to%20address%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noref