ass%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERampant%20urbanisation%20has%20destroyed%20water%20bodies%20in%20the%20city%3A%20Photo%20of%20Bagmane%20Tech%20Park%20taken%20in%20April%202013%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20impacts%20the%20lake%20system%2C%20and%20thereby%20the%20groundwater.%20We%20are%20one%20of%20the%20most%20intense%20borewelling%20communities%20in%20the%20world.%20Nowhere%20else%20will%20you%20see%20so%20many%20borewells%20being%20dug%20everywhere%2C%20which%20technically%20depletes%20all%20the%20groundwater%20reserves%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Arun%20Krishnamurthy%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F104777%2Ftamil-nadu-drought-nagapattinam%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EEnvironmentalist%20Foundation%20of%20India%20(EFI)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20revives%20water%20bodies.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWith%20groundwater%20reserves%20depleted%20and%20lakes%20holding%20sewage%2C%20which%20also%20means%20there%20is%20no%20space%20for%20freshwater%20from%20the%20monsoon%20rains%20to%20flow%20into%20%E2%80%94%20all%20these%20factors%20put%20together%20are%20causing%20this%20kind%20of%20drought.%20Bengaluru%20isn%E2%80%99t%20the%20first%20though%20given%20that%20Chennai%20went%20through%20something%20similar%20in%202018-19.%20Any%20urban%20pocket%20in%20India%20is%20bound%20to%20be%20affected%20by%20such%20a%20scenario%20given%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20a%20clear%20understanding%20of%20surface%20water%20bodies%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20how%20do%20you%20go%20about%20revving%20these%20water%20bodies%20and%20improving%20the%20groundwater%20level%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArun%20speaks%20of%20Devanahalli%20Kere%2C%20the%20first%20lake%20EFI%20took%20up%20in%20Bengaluru%20for%20revival%20in%202022.%20As%20an%20organisation%2C%20they%20have%20largely%20focussed%20on%20suburban%20Bengaluru%20rather%20than%20the%20main%20city%20area.%20This%20is%20because%20the%20suburban%20lakes%20were%20heading%20on%20the%20current%20path%20of%20the%20city%20lakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fr4iFfE90g_o%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3D0%26amp%3Brel%3D0%26amp%3Bfs%3D1%26amp%3Bplaysinline%3D1%26amp%3Bautohide%3D2%26amp%3Btheme%3Ddark%26amp%3Bcolor%3Dred%26amp%3Bcontrols%3D1%26amp%3B%5C%22%20data-origwidth%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20data-spai-excluded%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2Fr4iFfE90g_o%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTo%20prevent%20any%20kind%20of%20contamination%20or%20encroachment%2C%20we%20have%20taken%20up%20water%20bodies%20in%20Ramanagara%2C%20Tumkur%2C%20and%20Bengaluru%20(Rural)%20districts%2C%20and%20the%20closest%20such%20lake%20to%20the%20main%20city%20is%20the%20Devanahalli%20Lake.%20Within%20Karahalli%2C%20which%20is%20next%20to%20Devanahalli%2C%20we%20have%20revived%20at%20least%20five%20water%20bodies.%20What%20we%20have%20achieved%20is%20deepening%20these%20water%20bodies%20to%20increase%20storage%20capacity%2C%20regulating%20their%20inlet%20and%20outlet%20channels%20so%20that%20there%20is%20a%20free%20flow%20of%20water%2C%20and%20we%20have%20also%20ensured%20recharge%20wells%20have%20been%20created%20in%20all%20these%20systems%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Arun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBuilding%20these%20recharge%20wells%20is%20all%20about%20ensuring%20there%20is%20enough%20groundwater%20percolation.%20Creating%20a%20water%20holding%20structure%20based%20on%20the%20soil%20structure%2C%20understanding%20its%20utilisation%20value%20to%20the%20region%2C%20and%20creating%20percolation%20trenches%20and%20recharge%20wells%20have%20all%20been%20our%20key%20focus%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it%E2%80%99s%20in%20Devanahalli%2C%20Karahalli%2C%20the%20Baddihalli%20Lake%20in%20Tumkur%20city%2C%20or%20the%20Hulikunte%20lake.%20EFI%20has%20restored%20all%20these%20water%20bodies%20with%20this%20larger%20point%20in%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20the%20impact%20of%20all%20these%20initiatives%20on%20the%20communities%20who%20live%20near%20these%20lakes%20has%20been%20visible.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20borewells%20are%20not%20as%20dry%20as%20what%20we%20hear%20from%20other%20parts%20of%20the%20city.%20These%20lakes%2C%20which%20were%20often%20used%20as%20dumping%20sites%2C%20are%20now%20no%20longer%20perceived%20as%20such.%20People%20want%20to%20protect%20them.%20When%20droughts%20occur%2C%20people%20realise%20and%20understand%20the%20significance%20of%20these%20lakes%20better%20and%20they%20volunteer%20with%20us%20to%20maintain%20and%20upkeep%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20goes%20into%20the%20maintenance%20and%20upkeep%20of%20these%20water%20bodies%20includes%20the%20prevention%20of%20encroachment%2C%20dumping%20of%20garbage%2C%20and%20sewage%20entering%20that%20lake%2C%20and%20keeping%20an%20eye%20on%20the%20water%20body%20in%20general%20to%20maintain%20its%20quality%20and%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20it%E2%80%99s%20also%20important%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20canals%20interlinking%20these%20lakes%20are%20well%20maintained.%20As%20Arun%20notes%2C%20%E2%80%9CInterlinking%20of%20water%20bodies%20at%20an%20NGO%20level%20is%20impossible%20simply%20because%20between%20two%20lakes%2C%20the%20canal%20system%20that%20exists%20will%20largely%20fall%20under%20Government%20land%20or%20private%20land.%20We%20can%20recommend%20Government%20agencies%20to%20update%20these%20canal%20systems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20recommendations%20to%20the%20Government%20will%20also%20include%20properly%20mapping%20these%20water%20bodies%2C%20watershed%20wetlands%2C%20and%20preventing%20encroachment%20where%20necessary%20and%20focusing%20on%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20freshwater%20systems.%20We%20desperately%20need%20the%20latter%20today.%20But%20we%20will%20not%20be%20in%20a%20position%20to%20revive%20these%20interlinking%20areas%20completely%20simply%20because%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20the%20bandwidth%20to%20talk%20to%20all%20the%20landowners%20and%20remove%20encroachment%20or%20more.%20What%20is%20possible%20on%20our%20level%2C%20however%2C%20is%20inlet-outlet%20regulation%20within%20the%20lake%E2%80%99s%20periphery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAre%20lakes%20in%20the%20main%20city%20beyond%20redemption%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20not%20beyond%20redemption%20if%20there%20is%20a%20strong%20political%20will%2C%20heavy%20scientific%20backing%2C%20and%20complete%20community%20understanding%20of%20the%20problem.%20Even%20if%20one%20of%20these%20elements%20is%20missing%2C%20these%20lakes%20cannot%20be%20saved%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%5C%22%20data-epautoplay%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20data-facadesrc%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2FwEV7pANn0gw%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26amp%3Bautoplay%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_load_policy%3D0%26amp%3Bcc_lang_pref%3D%26amp%3Biv_load_policy%3D3%26amp%3Bloop%3D0%26amp%3Bmodestbranding%3